abstract: Barbara Dawson, woman who was arrested in Florida after refusing to leave hospital when she was discharged, dies from blood clot in her lung; Dawson had sought treatment for breathing difficulties and collapsed after arrest.
lead_paragraph: A woman who collapsed after the police arrested her for refusing to leave a hospital when doctors discharged her died from a blood clot in her lung.

headline.main: Florida: Woman Forced From Hospital Dies
